# .trivyignore — Trivy vulnerability suppressions
#
# This file contains CVEs that are known false positives or accepted risks.
# Each suppression must include:
#   - CVE ID (one per line)
#   - Date added (YYYY-MM-DD)
#   - Justification (why this CVE is not exploitable or is accepted risk)
#   - Reviewer (GitHub username who approved the suppression)
#
# Suppressions expire after 90 days and require re-review.
#
# Example format:
# CVE-2023-12345  # 2025-01-15 | Not exploitable: PDF parser internal only, no external input | Reviewer: @amos
#
# === ACTIVE SUPPRESSIONS ===
# (none yet)
